    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b6666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666",
      "key": "20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000005",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "A folyamat"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "M\u00F3dszertan, ami a \u003Cspan class=\u0022italic text-[#F7A5A5]\u0022\u003Egyakorlatban\u003C/span\u003E is m\u0171k\u00F6dik."
        },
        {
          "alias": "subtitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Nem hisz\u00FCnk az elm\u00E9leti, dobozos tr\u00E9ningekben. A mi megk\u00F6zel\u00EDt\u00E9s\u00FCnk a val\u00F3s kih\u00EDv\u00E1sokra \u00E9s azonnali akci\u00F3kra \u00E9p\u00FCl. A te temp\u00F3dban, a te \u00FCzleti c\u00E9ljaid\u00E9rt."
        },
        {
          "alias": "step1Num",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "01"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step1Title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Diagnosztika"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step1Desc",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Els\u0151 l\u00E9p\u00E9sk\u00E9nt pontosan felm\u00E9rj\u00FCk a jelenlegi vezet\u0151i kih\u00EDv\u00E1sokat, elakad\u00E1sokat \u00E9s a c\u00E9lokat egy struktur\u00E1lt, 90 perces m\u00E9lyinterj\u00FA sor\u00E1n."
        },
        {
          "alias": "step2Num",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "02"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step2Title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "K\u00F6z\u00F6s Tervez\u00E9s"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step2Desc",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Kialak\u00EDtunk egy teljesen egy\u00E9nre vagy csapatra szabott roadmapet, f\u00F3kusz\u00E1lva a kritikus beavatkoz\u00E1si pontokra \u00E9s a gyors gy\u0151zelmekre (quick wins)."
        },
        {
          "alias": "step3Num",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "03"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step3Title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Implement\u00E1ci\u00F3"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step3Desc",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "K\u00E9thetente tal\u00E1lkozunk: szitu\u00E1ci\u00F3s elemz\u00E9sek, d\u00F6nt\u00E9s-el\u0151k\u00E9sz\u00EDt\u00E9s \u00E9s azonnali, gyakorlatias visszajelz\u00E9sek a val\u00F3s napi probl\u00E9m\u00E1kra."
        },
        {
          "alias": "step4Num",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "04"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step4Title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "M\u00E9r\u00E9s \u0026 Korrekci\u00F3"
        },
        {
          "alias": "step4Desc",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Negyed\u00E9vente visszam\u00E9rj\u00FCk az eredm\u00E9nyeket a kit\u0171z\u00F6tt KPI-ok alapj\u00E1n, \u00E9s ha kell, finomhangoljuk az ir\u00E1nyt."
        },
        {
          "alias": "bottomStripTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "K\u00E9szen \u00E1llsz a szintl\u00E9p\u00E9sre?"
        },
        {
          "alias": "bottomStripDesc",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "K\u00E9rj egy k\u00F6tetlen, 30 perces egyeztet\u00E9st, ahol megvizsg\u00E1ljuk, miben tudunk a leggyorsabban seg\u00EDteni."
        },
        {
          "alias": "bottomStripCtaText",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Id\u0151pontot foglalok"
        },
        {
          "alias": "bottomStripCtaLink",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "#contact"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b7777777-7777-7777-7777-777777777777",
      "key": "20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000006",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Visszajelz\u00E9sek"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Amit a \u003Cspan class=\u0022italic text-[#F7A5A5]\u0022\u003Epartnereink\u003C/span\u003E mondanak."
        },
        {
          "alias": "subtitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "\u00DCgyfeleink nev\u00E9t \u00E9s c\u00E9g\u00E9t diszkr\u00E9ci\u00F3s okokb\u00F3l nem mindig v\u00E1llalhatjuk publikusan, de az eredm\u00E9nyeik maguk\u00E9rt besz\u00E9lnek."
        },
        {
          "alias": "t1Quote",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Az Executive Insights csapata nem csak elm\u00E9leti tan\u00E1csokat adott, hanem olyan gyakorlati megk\u00F6zel\u00EDt\u00E9st, amit azonnal be tudtam \u00E9p\u00EDteni a heti vezet\u0151i \u00E9rtekezletekbe. A csapatom dinamik\u00E1ja egy h\u00F3nap alatt \u00E9rezhet\u0151en javult."
        },
        {
          "alias": "t1Name",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Kov\u00E1cs G\u00E1bor"
        },
        {
          "alias": "t1Role",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Vez\u00E9rigazgat\u00F3, TechLogistics Kft."
        },
        {
          "alias": "t2Quote",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Egy kritikus c\u00E9gfelv\u00E1s\u00E1rl\u00E1s k\u00F6zep\u00E9n kerestem meg \u0151ket. A mentorom k\u00FCls\u0151, higgadt n\u00E9z\u0151pontja n\u00E9lk\u00FCl\u00F6zhetetlen volt ahhoz, hogy tiszt\u00E1n l\u00E1ssam a kock\u00E1zatokat \u00E9s ne csak az \u00E9rzelmeim vez\u00E9reljenek a t\u00E1rgyal\u00E1sokon."
        },
        {
          "alias": "t2Name",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "N. Andrea"
        },
        {
          "alias": "t2Role",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Alap\u00EDt\u00F3-tulajdonos, P\u00E9nz\u00FCgyi Szektor"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat1Number",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "94%"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat1Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Ism\u00E9telt megb\u00EDz\u00E1s"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat2Number",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "25\u002B"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat2Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sikeres C-level v\u00E1lt\u00E1s"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat3Number",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "15M\u20AC\u002B"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat3Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "\u00DCgyf\u00E9l \u00E1rbev\u00E9tel n\u00F6veked\u00E9s"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat4Number",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "0"
        },
        {
          "alias": "stat4Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Megszegett titoktart\u00E1s"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b0000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
      "key": "20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000007",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Azonnali, m\u00E9rhet\u0151 \u00E9rt\u00E9kteremt\u00E9s a menedzsmentben."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "b8888888-8888-8888-8888-888888888888",
      "key": "20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000008",
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "eyebrow",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Kapcsolat"
        },
        {
          "alias": "title",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Kezdj\u00FCk el a \u003Cspan class=\u0022italic text-[#F7A5A5]\u0022\u003Ek\u00F6z\u00F6s munk\u00E1t.\u003C/span\u003E"
        },
        {
          "alias": "subtitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Minden komoly elk\u00F6telez\u0151d\u00E9s egy ny\u00EDlt besz\u00E9lget\u00E9ssel kezd\u0151dik. Keress minket bizalommal!"
        },
        {
          "alias": "description",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Irod\u00E1nk Budapest sz\u00EDv\u00E9ben, diszkr\u00E9t k\u00F6rnyezetben tal\u00E1lhat\u00F3. A megkeres\u00E9seket 24 \u00F3r\u00E1n bel\u00FCl, teljes titoktart\u00E1s mellett kezelj\u00FCk."
        },
        {
          "alias": "c1Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Iroda"
        },
        {
          "alias": "c1Value",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "1051 Budapest, Sz\u00E9chenyi Istv\u00E1n t\u00E9r 7-8."
        },
        {
          "alias": "c2Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Email"
        },
        {
          "alias": "c2Value",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "hello@executiveinsights.hu"
        },
        {
          "alias": "c3Label",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Telefon"
        },
        {
          "alias": "c3Value",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "\u002B36 1 234 5678"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
